songs.title: Get Drunk
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
I am sleeping with your best friend
How do you like me now?
How do you like me now?

I am sleeping with your best friend
How do you like me now?
How do you like me now?

[Chorus]
Come on, get drunk
You know you wanna
I am, you can
Won't tell no one about it

It's gonna be a ball
It's gonna be a ball

[Verse 2]
I am lying, using again
Come on
It's gonna be a ball

[Chorus]
Come on, get drunk
You know you wanna
I am, you can
Won't tell no one about it

It's gonna be a ball
It's gonna be a ball

[Bridge]
Cigarettes, Robitussin
Will I ever get to heaven?
Cigarettes, Robitussin
Will I ever get to heaven?

It's not looking good now, ohh
It's not looking good now

[Outro]
Come on, get drunk
You know you wanna
Come on, get drunk
Get drunk
Get drunk

Get drunk
Get drunk
Get drunk
Get drunk
Get drunk
